Title: Jatt vs. Ielts
Actors: Anita Devgan, Hobby Dhaliwal, Mandeep Ghai, Gurpreet Ghuggi
Plot: In this hilarious laughter riot, a young man, like almost every other Punjabi, aspires to live his eternal Canadian dream. Struggling with his English and unable to clear the IELTS exam, he enrolls himself at an IELTS class.
